Class CraftInventoryProxy

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.craftbukkit.v1_8_R3.inventory.CraftInventory

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Proxy<org.bukkit.inventory.Inventory>, java.lang.Iterable<org.bukkit.inventory.ItemStack>, org.bukkit.inventory.Inventory

    public class CraftInventoryProxy
extends org.bukkit.craftbukkit.v1_8_R3.inventory.CraftInventory
implements Proxy<org.bukkit.inventory.Inventory>
    A Craft Inventory proxy class. To call methods in the base class, call the regular methods. To call methods from the current implementation, call the super_ methods.
